# تحليل معماري متقدم — Enterprise CyberNexus NGFW
## Production Blueprint — Fortinet / Palo Alto Class Architecture

> **المستوى:** Enterprise Production-Grade Architecture
> **المرجع:** Fortinet NGFW Architecture · Palo Alto PAN-OS Design Principles

---

## 1. 🧭 الفصل الأساسي: Control / Data / Intelligence Planes

> [!IMPORTANT]
> هذا الفصل هو **الركيزة الأولى** لأي NGFW حقيقي. بدونه النظام يصبح Monolith لا يمكن توسيعه.

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "🔵 Control Plane — العقل الإداري"
        CP1["⚙️ Policy Engine\n(Rule Compiler)"]
        CP2["🔌 Admin API\n(FastAPI / gRPC Gateway)"]
        CP3["🔐 Auth & RBAC\n(IAM / JWT / SPIFFE)"]
        CP4["📁 Config Manager\n(Versioned Config Store)"]
        CP5["🏗️ Cluster Manager\n(Leader Election / Raft)"]
    end

    subgraph "🔴 Data Plane — معالجة الحزم السريعة"
        DP1["⚡ eBPF/XDP Layer\n(Kernel-Level Filtering)"]
        DP2["🔄 L4/L7 Proxy Engine\n(Zero-Copy Forwarding)"]
        DP3["🔍 Stateful DPI Engine\n(Pipeline / Plugins)"]
        DP4["📡 Connection Tracker\n(ConnTrack)"]
        DP5["🔐 TLS Interception\n(Inline SSL Inspection)"]
    end

    subgraph "🟣 Intelligence Plane — الذكاء والتحليل"
        IP1["🧠 ML Inference Engine\n(ONNX Runtime)"]
        IP2["📊 Behavioral Analytics\n(UBA Engine)"]
        IP3["🌐 Threat Correlation\n(Graph Engine)"]
        IP4["🎯 Threat Scoring\n(Risk Aggregator)"]
        IP5["📡 Threat Intel\n(AbuseIPDB / OTX)"]
    end

    subgraph "📊 Observability Plane"
        OB1["📈 Prometheus\n(Metrics)"]
        OB2["📝 Loki / ELK\n(Logs)"]
        OB3["🔭 OpenTelemetry\n(Tracing)"]
        OB4["📉 Grafana\n(Dashboards)"]
    end

    CP1 -->|"Compile Rules → Push"| DP1 & DP3
    CP2 -->|"Admin Commands"| CP1 & CP4 & CP5
    DP3 -->|"Events & Scores"| IP3 & IP2
    IP1 & IP4 -->|"AI Decision"| DP3
    DP1 & DP3 & IP1 -->|"Metrics / Traces / Logs"| OB1 & OB2 & OB3

    EB["⚡ Event Bus\n(NATS / Kafka)"]
    DP3 <-->|"Async Events"| EB
    IP3 <-->|"Async Events"| EB
    CP1 <-->|"Policy Updates"| EB
```

> [!NOTE]
> **القاعدة الذهبية:** Control Plane لا يلمس الـ Traffic أبداً. Data Plane لا يتخذ قرارات Policy بنفسه. Intelligence Plane لا يوقف Traffic مباشرة — يُعطي فقط "قرارات" (Decisions) للـ Data Plane.

