## 3. 🧠 ML Pipeline الكامل (Production Grade)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph "1️⃣ Feature Extraction Layer"
        FE1["📦 Packet Features\n(size, TTL, flags)"]
        FE2["🌊 Flow Features\n(duration, bytes/pkt)"]
        FE3["🔍 DNS Features\n(entropy, query length)"]
        FE4["🔐 TLS Fingerprint\n(JA3 / JA4 hash)"]
    end

    subgraph "2️⃣ Stream Processing"
        SP["⚡ Async Feature Aggregator\n(Sliding Window / Flink-style)"]
    end

    subgraph "3️⃣ Model Registry"
        MR1["📦 Model v1.0 — Malware Classifier"]
        MR2["📦 Model v2.1 — WAF NLP"]
        MR3["📦 Model v3.0 — Behavioral (UBA)"]
        MR_META["🗂️ Registry Metadata\n(version, performance, rollback)"]
    end

    subgraph "4️⃣ Inference Service"
        IS["🚀 ONNX Runtime / TensorRT\nREST + gRPC API\nGPU Optional"]
        CACHE["⚡ Prediction Cache\n(LRU, 100ms TTL)"]
    end

    subgraph "5️⃣ Feedback Loop"
        FL1["👨‍💻 Analyst Labeling\n(False positive review)"]
        FL2["🔄 Auto Retraining\n(Weekly pipeline)"]
        FL3["📊 Model Performance\n(Drift detection)"]
    end

    FE1 & FE2 & FE3 & FE4 --> SP
    SP --> IS
    MR1 & MR2 & MR3 --> IS
    IS --> CACHE
    IS -->|"inference result"| DPI["To DPI Pipeline"]
    FL1 & FL3 --> FL2
    FL2 -->|"new model version"| MR_META
    MR_META --> MR1 & MR2 & MR3
```

**Model Deployment Strategy:**
| Strategy | الوصف | متى تستخدمه |
|---|---|---|
| **Blue/Green** | نسختان شغّالتان، تبديل فوري | rollback سريع |
| **Canary** | 5% traffic للنموذج الجديد | اختبار التأثير أمان |
| **Shadow** | النموذج الجديد يعمل بدون تأثير | مقارنة الأداء |
| **A/B Test** | مقارنة controlled بين نموذجين | قياس دقة |

