```

**KPIs المُراقَبة:**
| Metric | Target | Alert Threshold |
|---|---|---|
| `packets_per_second` | > 1M pps | < 500K pps |
| `l7_latency_p99` | < 200µs | > 500µs |
| `drop_rate` | < 0.1% | > 1% |
| `ai_inference_latency` | < 5ms | > 20ms |
| `pipeline_queue_depth` | < 1000 | > 5000 |
| `module_crash_count` | 0 | > 0 per hour |

