## 5. 🛡️ Security Hardening Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "External Boundary"
        EXT["🌐 Internet / Client"]
        GW["🔌 API Gateway\n(Rate Limit + WAF + Schema)"]
    end

    subgraph "Internal Services (mTLS Mesh)"
        API["FastAPI Service"]
        ML_SVC["ML Inference Service"]
        CORR["Correlation Engine"]
        DB_SVC["Database Service"]
    end

    subgraph "Identity Layer (Zero Trust)"
        CERT["🔐 Internal CA\n(short-lived certs, 24h)"]
        SPIFFE["🪪 SPIFFE Identity\n(workload identity)"]
    end

    EXT -->|"HTTPS (TLS 1.3)"| GW
    GW -->|"rate limit: 100 req/s/IP\nJWT validation\nschema check"| API
    
    API <-->|"mTLS"| ML_SVC
    API <-->|"mTLS"| CORR
    API <-->|"mTLS"| DB_SVC
    
    CERT --> API & ML_SVC & CORR & DB_SVC
    SPIFFE --> CERT
```

**طبقات الحماية:**
| الطبقة | الآلية | الغرض |
|---|---|---|
| **Rate Limiting** | Token Bucket (100 req/s/IP) | منع brute force |
| **mTLS** | شهادات داخلية قصيرة (24h) | تشفير الديني |
| **Schema Validation** | Pydantic strict mode | منع injection |
| **JWT + RBAC** | RS256 + 15min expiry | التحكم بالوصول |
| **DDoS (SYN Flood)** | eBPF SYN cookie | kernel-level protection |
| **Input Sanitization** | HTML escape + regex | XSS / SQLi منع |

---

## 6. 🧩 Failure Handling & Resilience

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Normal: System Start

    Normal --> Degraded: Module Failure detected
    Normal --> FailOpen: Data Plane crash
    Normal --> FailClose: Critical security failure

    Degraded --> Normal: Module recovered
    Degraded --> FailOpen: Cascade failure

    FailOpen --> Normal: Manual intervention
    FailClose --> Normal: Admin override required

    state Normal {
        [*] --> Active
        Active --> [*]: All modules healthy
    }

    state Degraded {
        [*] --> FallbackRules
        FallbackRules --> [*]: AI down → hardcoded rule engine
    }

    state FailOpen {
        note: Traffic passes without DPI
        note: Alert sent immediately
    }

    state FailClose {
        note: All traffic blocked
        note: Emergency alert
    }
```

**سياسات المرونة:**
| المكوِّن | فشل مؤقت | فشل كامل | الاسترداد |
|---|---|---|---|
| **eBPF Layer** | تعطل XDP → iptables fallback | Fail-Open | تلقائي عند إعادة الإقلاع |
| **AI Module** | Retry x3 → rule-based fallback | Degraded mode | إعادة تحميل النموذج |
| **Event Bus** | Buffer locally | Degraded mode | اتصال تلقائي |
| **DPI Pipeline** | إنهاء الـ plugin → تخطيه | Circuit Breaker | hot reload |
| **Database** | Connection pool retry | قراءة من Cache | reconnect auto |

**Circuit Breaker Pattern:**
```
CLOSED → [5 failures / 10s] → OPEN (reject calls)
OPEN → [30s timeout] → HALF-OPEN (test call)
HALF-OPEN → [success] → CLOSED | [fail] → OPEN
```

