## 8. 🧱 Data Schemas (Core Domain Models)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    PACKET {
        string id
        string src_ip
        string dst_ip
        int src_port
        int dst_port
        string protocol
        int length
        timestamp captured_at
        bytes raw_payload
    }

    INSPECTION_CONTEXT {
        string session_id
        string identity_type
        string user_id
        string device_fingerprint
        float risk_score
        bool is_decrypted
        string geo_country
        timestamp created_at
    }

    SECURITY_EVENT {
        string id
        string event_type
        string rule_id
        float confidence
        string severity
        string src_ip
        string dst_ip
        json raw_evidence
        timestamp detected_at
    }

    FIREWALL_RULE {
        int id
        string name
        string action
        string source_ip
        string dest_ip
        string protocol
        string dest_port
        int priority
        int hit_count
        bool is_critical
        timestamp created_at
    }

    POLICY {
        string id
        string version
        string name
        json rules_snapshot
        string created_by
        timestamp activated_at
        bool is_active
    }

    PACKET ||--o{ INSPECTION_CONTEXT : "enriches"
    INSPECTION_CONTEXT ||--o{ SECURITY_EVENT : "triggers"
    FIREWALL_RULE }o--|| POLICY : "belongs_to"
    SECURITY_EVENT }o--o| FIREWALL_RULE : "matched_by"
```

