## 9. ⚙️ Configuration Management System

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "Config Sources (Priority Order)"
        ENV["🔧 Environment Variables\n(highest priority)"]
        FILE["📁 base.yaml\n(file config)"]
        DB_CFG["🗄️ DB Config Store\n(dynamic settings)"]
        DEFAULT["📋 Defaults\n(lowest priority)"]
    end

    subgraph "Config Manager"
        LOADER["📥 Config Loader\n(merge + validate)"]
        SCHEMA["✅ Schema Validator\n(Pydantic)"]
        STORE["💾 Config Store\n(in-memory)"]
        WATCHER["👁️ File Watcher\n(inotify)"]
    end

    subgraph "Hot Reload Pipeline"
        CHANGE["config.changed event"]
        VALIDATE["Validate new config"]
        DIFF["Compute diff"]
        APPLY["Apply changed keys only\n(no restart needed)"]
        SNAPSHOT["📸 Snapshot for rollback"]
    end

    ENV & FILE & DB_CFG & DEFAULT --> LOADER
    LOADER --> SCHEMA --> STORE
    WATCHER -->|"File changed"| CHANGE
    CHANGE --> VALIDATE --> DIFF --> APPLY --> SNAPSHOT
```

**Config Versioning:**
| Feature | الوصف |
|---|---|
| **Snapshots** | كل تغيير ينشئ snapshot محفوظ |
| **Rollback** | `config rollback --version=12` |
| **Diff** | مقارنة بين إصدارَين |
| **Env Separation** | `config.dev.yaml` / `config.prod.yaml` |
| **Secrets Management** | قيم حساسة في Vault أو env vars فقط |

