## 11. 🔐 PKI & Certificate Lifecycle

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant ADMIN as 👨‍💻 Admin
    participant CA    as 🔐 Root CA
    participant INTER as 📜 Intermediate CA
    participant GW   as 🌐 SSL Gateway
    participant CLIENT as 💻 Client

    ADMIN->>CA: Generate Root CA (Ed25519, 10yr)
    CA-->>ADMIN: rootCA.pem
    ADMIN->>CLIENT: Install rootCA.pem (trust anchor)

    loop Daily Certificate Rotation
        GW->>INTER: CSR for inspection cert
        INTER->>CA: Sign with intermediate key
        CA-->>INTER: Signed cert (24h validity)
        INTER-->>GW: Deploy new cert (zero downtime)
    end

    CLIENT->>GW: HTTPS Request
    GW->>GW: SSL Bump → re-sign with CA
    GW-->>CLIENT: Signed by our CA (trusted)

    Note over GW,CLIENT: OCSP Stapling — GW checks revocation
    GW->>CA: OCSP Request
    CA-->>GW: OCSP Response (cached 1hr)
```

**Certificate Hierarchy:**
```
Root CA (offline, 10 years, Ed25519)
  └── Intermediate CA (online, 1 year)
        ├── TLS Inspection CA (24h, auto-rotate)
        ├── Internal Services CA (30d, mTLS)
        └── Admin Portal CA (90d)
```

---

## 12. 🧩 Plugin System Design (Enterprise Safe)

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "Plugin Lifecycle"
        LOAD["📦 Load Plugin\n(.py file / WASM)"]
        VALIDATE["✅ Validate Manifest\n(version, API compat)"]
        SANDBOX["🔒 Sandbox Init\n(restricted Python env)"]
        ACTIVATE["🟢 Activate\n(register with Pipeline)"]
        HOT["🔄 Hot Reload\n(zero downtime swap)"]
        UNLOAD["🔴 Unload\n(graceful shutdown)"]
    end

    subgraph "Sandbox Restrictions"
        R1["❌ No network.socket()"]
        R2["❌ No os.system()"]
        R3["❌ No filesystem write"]
        R4["❌ No subprocess"]
        R5["✅ Controlled APIs only\n(inspect, log, score)"]
    end

    subgraph "Plugin API Contract"
        API_IN["def inspect(context: InspectionContext)"]
        API_OUT["returns: InspectionResult(action, score, reason)"]
        API_CB["def on_config_reload(new_cfg)"]
        API_HLT["def health_check() → bool"]
    end

    LOAD --> VALIDATE --> SANDBOX --> ACTIVATE
    ACTIVATE -->|"live traffic"| HOT
    HOT --> UNLOAD

    SANDBOX --> R1 & R2 & R3 & R4 & R5
    ACTIVATE --> API_IN & API_OUT & API_CB & API_HLT
```

**Plugin Version Compatibility:**
```
Plugin Manifest:
  name: "malware_av"
  version: "2.1.0"
  api_version: ">=3.0, <4.0"   ← must match Pipeline API version
  requires: ["ml_core>=1.5"]
```

