## 13. 🌐 Threat Intelligence Integration

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph "🌍 External Feeds"
        F1["AbuseIPDB\n(IP reputation)"]
        F2["AlienVault OTX\n(IOC / malware)"]
        F3["Emerging Threats\n(signatures)"]
        F4["Custom TAXII\n(enterprise feed)"]
    end

    subgraph "🔄 Ingestion Pipeline"
        FETCH["⏱️ Scheduled Fetcher\n(every 15 min)"]
        NORM["🔧 Normalizer\n(STIX 2.1 format)"]
        DEDUP["🔍 Deduplicator\n(SHA256 matching)"]
        SCORE["📊 Enricher\n(confidence + age score)"]
    end

    subgraph "💾 Intel Store"
        IP_REP["📊 IP Reputation DB\n(Redis HSet — O(1) lookup)"]
        DOMAIN_REP["🔍 Domain Reputation DB\n(Bloom Filter + exact)"]
        IOC["🗂️ IOC Store\n(file hashes, patterns)"]
    end

    subgraph "Integration Points"
        FW_CHK["🛡️ Firewall ACL Check"]
        DNS_CHK["🔍 DNS Security Check"]
        MAL_CHK["🦠 Malware Hash Check"]
    end

    F1 & F2 & F3 & F4 --> FETCH --> NORM --> DEDUP --> SCORE
    SCORE --> IP_REP & DOMAIN_REP & IOC
    IP_REP --> FW_CHK
    DOMAIN_REP --> DNS_CHK
    IOC --> MAL_CHK
```

