## 14. 🚀 Performance Engineering Targets

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Performance Goals"
        T1["🎯 Throughput\n10–40 Gbps per node"]
        T2["⚡ L4 Latency\n< 10 µs (eBPF path)"]
        T3["🔍 L7 Latency (p99)\n< 200 µs"]
        T4["🧠 AI Inference\n< 5 ms"]
        T5["💾 Memory / Core\n< 512 MB per worker"]
    end

    subgraph "Optimizations"
        O1["CPU Pinning\n(isolcpus + taskset)"]
        O2["NUMA-Aware Alloc\n(numactl --membind)"]
        O3["Batch Processing\n(64 packets per batch)"]
        O4["Zero-Copy Buffers\n(AF_XDP / io_uring)"]
        O5["Lock-Free Queues\n(SPSC ring buffer)"]
        O6["Prediction Cache\n(LRU 100ms TTL)"]
    end

    T1 --> O3 & O4
    T2 --> O1 & O5
    T3 --> O2 & O6
    T4 --> O6
    T5 --> O2
```

**Load Testing Strategy:**

| Test | Tool | السيناريو | المعيار |
|---|---|---|---|
| Throughput | `iperf3 + pktgen` | 10M packets/s اصطناعية | > 1M pps |
| Latency | `hping3` | RTT measurement | p99 < 200µs |
| Stress (L7) | `wrk2` + `h2load` | HTTP/2 flood | no crash at 100K req/s |
| AI Inference | `locust` | 1000 concurrent inference calls | p99 < 5ms |
| HA Failover | Manual kill + tcpdump | Node crash → reconnect | < 3s |

