| Plugin System (Sandbox/WASM) | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ (PAN-OS Apps) |
| mTLS Internal Services | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Threat Intel Integration | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Smart Policy Optimizer | ✅ **unique** | ❌ | ❌ |
| Active-Active Config/HA Sync | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Open Source / Customizable | ✅ **unique** | ❌ | ❌ |

